119 {
120 get
121 {

470 internal XsdValidatingReader(XmlReader reader, XmlResolver xmlResolver, XmlReaderSettings readerSettings, XmlSchemaObject partialValidationType)
471 {
472 _coreReader = reader;
473 _coreReaderNSResolver = reader as IXmlNamespaceResolver;
474 _lineInfo = reader as IXmlLineInfo;
475 _coreReaderNameTable = _coreReader.NameTable;
476 if (_coreReaderNSResolver == null)
477 {
478 _nsManager = new XmlNamespaceManager(_coreReaderNameTable);
479 _manageNamespaces = true;
480 }
481 _thisNSResolver = this;
482 _xmlResolver = xmlResolver;
483 _processInlineSchema = (readerSettings.ValidationFlags & XmlSchemaValidationFlags.ProcessInlineSchema) != 0;
484 _validationState = ValidatingReaderState.Init;
485 _defaultAttributes = new ArrayList();
486 _currentAttrIndex = -1;
487 _attributePSVINodes = new AttributePSVIInfo[8];
488 _valueGetter = GetStringValue;
489 s_typeOfString = typeof(string);
490 _xmlSchemaInfo = new XmlSchemaInfo();
491 _nsXmlNs = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/");
492 _nsXs = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema");
493 _nsXsi = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance");
494 _xsiType = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("type");
495 _xsiNil = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("nil");
496 _xsiSchemaLocation = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("schemaLocation");
497 _xsiNoNamespaceSchemaLocation = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("noNamespaceSchemaLocation");
498 _xsdSchema = _coreReaderNameTable.Add("schema");
499 SetupValidator(readerSettings, reader, partialValidationType);
500 _validationEvent = readerSettings.GetEventHandler();
501 }

508 [MemberNotNull("_validator")]
509 private void SetupValidator(XmlReaderSettings readerSettings, XmlReader reader, XmlSchemaObject partialValidationType)
510 {
511 _validator = new XmlSchemaValidator(_coreReaderNameTable, readerSettings.Schemas, _thisNSResolver, readerSettings.ValidationFlags);
512 _validator.XmlResolver = _xmlResolver;
513 _validator.SourceUri = XmlConvert.ToUri(reader.BaseURI);
514 _validator.ValidationEventSender = this;
515 _validator.ValidationEventHandler += readerSettings.GetEventHandler();
516 _validator.LineInfoProvider = _lineInfo;
517 if (_validator.ProcessSchemaHints)
518 {
519 _validator.SchemaSet.ReaderSettings.DtdProcessing = readerSettings.DtdProcessing;
520 }
521 _validator.SetDtdSchemaInfo(reader.DtdInfo);
522 if (partialValidationType != null)
523 {
524 _validator.Initialize(partialValidationType);
525 }
526 else
527 {
528 _validator.Initialize();
529 }

753 public override object ReadContentAs(Type returnType, IXmlNamespaceResolver namespaceResolver)
754 {
755 if (!XmlReader.CanReadContentAs(NodeType))
756 {
757 throw CreateReadContentAsException("ReadContentAs");
758 }
759 string originalStringValue;
760 object value = InternalReadContentAsObject(unwrapTypedValue: false, out originalStringValue);
761 XmlSchemaType xmlSchemaType = ((NodeType == XmlNodeType.Attribute) ? AttributeXmlType : ElementXmlType);
762 try
763 {
764 if (xmlSchemaType != null)
765 {
766 if (returnType == typeof(DateTimeOffset) && xmlSchemaType.Datatype is Datatype_dateTimeBase)
767 {
768 value = originalStringValue;
769 }
770 return xmlSchemaType.ValueConverter.ChangeType(value, returnType);
771 }
772 return XmlUntypedConverter.Untyped.ChangeType(value, returnType, namespaceResolver);
773 }
774 catch (FormatException innerException)
775 {
776 throw new XmlException(System.SR.Xml_ReadContentAsFormatException, returnType.ToString(), innerException, this);
